 系统设置 里面设置，如果扫码枪没有解到码，反馈给 OEM的信号，如下图：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"864f937a-a4e8-4dfc-866a-d342270545b0","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-2"},{"bbox":[88,370,505,692],"index":3,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/8a33532cae579aa589b744c1075f3be363adea789309a5f67849ebf90478631d.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.7008403361344537,"page_idx":3,"id":"ac8885ed-443b-486c-9afb-059cde5b7067","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-3"},{"bbox":[148,703,508,752],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":4,"text":"注意：通讯指令与反馈指令都是根据 OEM 软件里写的得来，一定要相同一致。","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":3,"id":"3ffa5c3c-6efc-47f7-ae9a-b913dfb4b6b2","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"3-4"}],[{"bbox":[20,2,129,20],"index":0,"angle":0,"type":"image_caption","text":"2.检出数根格术","id":"bac44b95-1b86-4bd6-937e-3a75db80da57","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":4,"page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-0"},{"bbox":[0,9,581,833],"index":1,"angle":0,"type":"image","img_path":"/6af8274c656683736eaf29c60af6401008e1e7adfe357596a36e002d65bafbc1.jpg","color":{"line":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)","fill":"rgba(89, 92, 220, 1)"},"img_ratio":0.9764705882352941,"page_idx":4,"id":"1b10e38e-572d-4c03-98af-412d4bd8e784","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"4-1"}],[{"bbox":[49,12,196,34],"type":"title","angle":0,"index":0,"text":"# 四．配置的调试","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"level":1,"page_idx":5,"id":"54f270ca-61f2-4d6d-adab-4106384cc4d6","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"5-0"},{"bbox":[67,46,351,63],"type":"text","angle":0,"index":1,"text":"设置 $\\twoheadrightarrow$ 读取设置 进入配置调试界面，如下图：","color":{"line":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)","fill":"rgba(13, 83, 222, 1)"},"page_idx":5,"id":"80d860e7-5dda-4391-92ed-b603501bd140","page_size":[595,842],"block_position":"5-1"},{"bbox":[81,67,